headline.main: Trump Win Probably Didn’t Cause Canadian Immigration Website’s Crash
headline.print_headline: Trump Win Probably Didn’t Cause Canadian Immigration Website’s Crash

lead_paragraph: The malfunction on election night was linked on social media to despondent Americans hoping to emigrate. It was more likely an unrelated travel program deadline.
